      <title>马杜罗承诺尊重巴西对阿根廷大使馆的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/milei-thanks-brazil-for-stepping-in-amid-venezuela-embassy-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情的巴西官员透露，委内瑞拉向巴西承诺，将尊重阿根廷驻加拉加斯大使馆的完整性，包括在外交使团内避难的六名尼古拉斯·马杜罗政府反对者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/milei-thanks-brazil-for-stepping-in-amid-venezuela-embassy-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 13:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
